---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Full-Stack Software Engineer with expertise in Java, React, and AI-powered applications",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-12">About Me</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p class="text-lg">
			I'm a Full-Stack Software Engineer pursuing my Master's in Computer Science at Youngstown State University 
			with a perfect 4.0 GPA. I specialize in building scalable, high-performance applications using modern 
			technologies like Java Spring Boot, React, and AI/ML frameworks.
		</p>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">What I Do</h2>
		<p>
			I create end-to-end solutions that bridge the gap between complex backend systems and intuitive user 
			interfaces. My experience spans from developing microservices architectures to implementing AI-powered 
			features that enhance user experiences.
		</p>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Professional Experience</h2>
		<p>
			During my internship at Muvzen, I contributed to building production-grade microservices that improved 
			system response times by 35%. I worked extensively with:
		</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>Designing and implementing RESTful APIs with Spring Boot</li>
			<li>Building responsive dashboards with React and TypeScript</li>
			<li>Implementing secure authentication systems (JWT, OAuth2.0)</li>
			<li>Optimizing database performance with PostgreSQL and MongoDB</li>
			<li>Setting up CI/CD pipelines and containerization with Docker</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Technical Expertise</h2>
		<p>
			I'm proficient in full-stack development with a strong foundation in both traditional and modern 
			technologies:
		</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li><strong>Backend:</strong> Java Spring Boot, Node.js, Express.js, REST APIs, WebSocket</li>
			<li><strong>Frontend:</strong> React, Redux, Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS</li>
			<li><strong>Databases:</strong> PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis</li>
			<li><strong>AI/ML:</strong> TensorFlow, PyTorch, LangChain, OpenAI API integration</li>
			<li><strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, Git</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Notable Projects</h2>
		<p>
			I've built several full-stack applications that demonstrate my ability to work with cutting-edge 
			technologies:
		</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>
				<strong>Dev Collab:</strong> An AI-powered collaboration hub with real-time messaging, LLM integration 
				for auto-summarization, and OAuth2.0 security
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Smart Energy Platform:</strong> An IoT monitoring system handling 10K+ daily data points with 
				hybrid database architecture and role-based access control
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Education & Learning</h2>
		<p>
			Currently pursuing my Master's degree at Youngstown State University, I maintain a 4.0 GPA while 
			continuously expanding my knowledge in web development, database systems, software engineering, and 
			data structures. I'm passionate about staying current with emerging technologies and best practices 
			in software development.
		</p>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">What Drives Me</h2>
		<p>
			I'm passionate about solving complex problems with elegant, efficient solutions. Whether it's optimizing 
			database queries, implementing real-time features, or integrating AI capabilities, I approach each 
			challenge with curiosity and determination. I believe in writing clean, maintainable code and following 
			industry best practices.
		</p>

		<h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Let's Connect</h2>
		<p>
			I'm always interested in discussing new opportunities, collaborating on interesting projects, or simply 
			connecting with fellow developers. Feel free to reach out through any of the social links on this site, 
			or send me an email directly.
		</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
